      </p>
      <p class="mt-10 text-gray">
        Are you seeking security and peace of mind in legal decision-making? At
        Lexdata Services, our mission is to provide you with the legal certainty
        you need to make informed and strategic decisions. We combine deep legal
        knowledge with a solid network of relationships, offering innovative,
        agile, and efficient solutions tailored to your specific requirements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-10 bg-secondary-background w-[70%] ml-auto p-6">
    <div class="w-[75%] leading-6">
      <p class="mb-4 font-bold">Our specialization encompasses:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc flex flex-col gap-4">
        <li class="text-black/50">
          <span class="font-bold text-black">Real Estate: </span>We ensure the profitability and legality of your real estate investments through comprehensive and expert management.
        </li>
        <li class="text-black/50">
          <span class="font-bold text-black"
            >Mandates and Powers of Attorney:
          </span>We protect your interests and guarantee the fulfillment of your intentions, providing precise and reliable legal advice.
        </li>
        <li class="text-black/50">
          <span class="font-bold text-black">Family Law: </span>We accompany you with sensitivity and professionalism in resolving family conflicts. For your travels, we manage exit permits for your minor children, prioritizing your family's well-being.
        </li>
        <li class="text-black/50">
          <span class="font-bold text-black">Corporate Law: </span>We advise you clearly on business models and sponsor the corporate structure that best suits your needs, whether it's a limited company, corporation, or civil and commercial partnership.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<Banner image={"catalejo.webp"} />
