      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto mt-10">
    <div class="w-[70%] mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div
          class="border-l-8 border-l-olive p-4 w-[30%] flex flex-col items-end text-4xl text-olive"
        >
          <!-- <p class="text-olive text-6xl text-left">¿Qué nos diferencia?</p> -->
          <div>WHAT</div>
          <div>SETS US</div>
          <div>APART?</div>
        </div>
        <hr class="border-t-3 border-dotted w-26 rotate-90" />
        <div class="w-[50%]">
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            At Lexdata Services, we integrate traditional legal experience with advanced technological solutions, offering personalized and optimized service, ensuring maximum security and efficiency in all your operations.
